"title": "5503: rich, the",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5503",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>It is hard but not impossible for rich people to enter God's kingdom. They must put their hope in God, not in their riches. Rich people who live selfishly, abuse their position and fail to repent and live for Jesus Christ, are in peril.</p>\n<h2>Parables concerning rich people</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam12:1-2Sam12:10\">2SA 12:1–12:10</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt13:44-Matt13:46\">MAT 13:44–13:46</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt18:23\">MAT 18:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt22:2\">MAT 22:2</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke14:16\">LUK 14:16</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt25:14\">MAT 25:14</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke19:12\">LUK 19:12</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke12:16\">LUK 12:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke15:11-Luke15:13\">LUK 15:11–15:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke16:1\">LUK 16:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke18:10\">LUK 18:10</a></p>\n<h2>Rich people have received blessing</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim6:17\">1TI 6:17</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps1:3\">PSA 1:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps112:1-Ps112:3\">PSA 112:1–112:3</a></p>\n<h3>They have friends</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov14:20\">PRO 14:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov19:4\">PRO 19:4</a></p>\n<h3>They have power</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov22:7\">PRO 22:7</a></p>\n<h3>They have security</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov10:15\">PRO 10:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov18:11\">PRO 18:11</a></p>\n<h2>Warnings to rich people</h2>\n<h3>They should recognise that God is the giver of riches</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut8:17-Deut8:18\">DEU 8:17–8:18</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut32:13-Deut32:15\">DEU 32:13–32:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos2:8\">HOS 2:8</a></p>\n<h3>They should not be arrogant or complacent on account of their riches</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer9:23-Jer9:24\">JER 9:23–9:24</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps49:5-Ps49:6\">PSA 49:5–49:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer49:4\">JER 49:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos12:8\">HOS 12:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim6:17\">1TI 6:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev3:17\">REV 3:17</a></p>\n<h3>They should not trust in their riches</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov11:28\">PRO 11:28</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps49:6\">PSA 49:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps52:7\">PSA 52:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps62:10\">PSA 62:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer48:7\">JER 48:7</a></p>\n<h3>They face disaster if they lack wisdom</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps49:20\">PSA 49:20</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov28:11\">PRO 28:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer9:23-Jer9:24\">JER 9:23–9:24</a></p>\n<h3>They must live moral lives</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov28:6\">PRO 28:6</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov22:16\">PRO 22:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer5:27-Jer5:28\">JER 5:27–5:28</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer17:11\">JER 17:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic6:12\">MIC 6:12</a></p>\n<h3>Wealth can bring anxiety</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl5:12\">ECC 5:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt6:25-Matt6:34\">MAT 6:25–6:34</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke12:22-Luke12:31\">LUK 12:22–12:31</a></p>\n<h3>Riches are of fleeting value</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke12:16-Luke12:21\">LUK 12:16–12:21</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps49:5-Ps49:12\">PSA 49:5–49:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov27:24\">PRO 27:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl5:15\">ECC 5:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa10:3\">ISA 10:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt6:19\">MAT 6:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim6:7\">1TI 6:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job1:21\">JOB 1:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas1:10-Jas1:11\">JAS 1:10–1:11</a></p>\n<h3>Ultimate security is found in God alone</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod15:2\">EXO 15:2</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam22:33\">2SA 22:33</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr16:11\">1CH 16:11</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps28:7\">PSA 28:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps29:11\">PSA 29:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps46:1\">PSA 46:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps52:6-Ps52:7\">PSA 52:6–52:7</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa12:2\">ISA 12:2</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hab3:19\">HAB 3:19</a></p>\n<h3>It is hard for rich people to enter God's kingdom</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt19:23-Matt19:26\">MAT 19:23–19:26</a></strong> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark10:23-Mark10:27\">MRK 10:23–10:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke18:24-Luke18:27\">LUK 18:24–18:27</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt13:22\">MAT 13:22</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark4:18-Mark4:19\">MRK 4:18–4:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke8:14\">LUK 8:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt19:16-Matt19:22\">MAT 19:16–19:22</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark10:17-Mark10:22\">MRK 10:17–10:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke18:18-Luke18:23\">LUK 18:18–18:23</a></p>\n<h2>Rich people will be judged for their behaviour</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech11:5-Zech11:6\">ZEC 11:5–11:6</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke1:53\">LUK 1:53</a></p>\n<h3>If they exploit, oppress or kill the poor</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas5:1-Jas5:4\">JAS 5:1–5:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov14:31\">PRO 14:31</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov22:16\">PRO 22:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov28:3\">PRO 28:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek18:12-Ezek18:13\">EZK 18:12–18:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek22:29-Ezek22:31\">EZK 22:29–22:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas2:6\">JAS 2:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas5:6\">JAS 5:6</a></p>\n<h3>If they hoard wealth and live selfishly</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas5:5\">JAS 5:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke12:16-Luke12:21\">LUK 12:16–12:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke16:19-Luke16:31\">LUK 16:19–16:31</a></p>\n<h3>If they slander the name of Jesus Christ</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas2:7\">JAS 2:7</a></p>\n<h2>Commands to rich people</h2>\n<h3>To seek God's kingdom as first priority</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt6:19-Matt6:21\">MAT 6:19–6:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt6:31-Matt6:33\">MAT 6:31–6:33</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke12:29-Luke12:31\">LUK 12:29–12:31</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim6:19\">1TI 6:19</a></p>\n<h3>To repent from sin</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev3:17\">REV 3:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev3:19\">REV 3:19</a></p>\n<h3>To be generous towards the needy</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim6:18\">1TI 6:18</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt19:21\">MAT 19:21</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark10:21\">MRK 10:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke18:22\">LUK 18:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke3:11\">LUK 3:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke11:41\">LUK 11:41</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke12:33-Luke12:34\">LUK 12:33–12:34</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke14:12-Luke14:14\">LUK 14:12–14:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke16:9\">LUK 16:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke19:8\">LUK 19:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor8:1-2Cor8:5\">2CO 8:1–8:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor8:9\">2CO 8:9</a> <em>Jesus Christ's example the motivation for generosity</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor8:13-2Cor8:15\">2CO 8:13–8:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor9:6-2Cor9:15\">2CO 9:6–9:15</a></p>\n<h2>Incorrect attitudes to the rich</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl10:20\">ECC 10:20</a> <em>cursing them</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps49:16-Ps49:17\">PSA 49:16–49:17</a> <em>living in awe of them</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps49:5-Ps49:6\">PSA 49:5–49:6</a> <em>fearing them</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job34:18-Job34:19\">JOB 34:18–34:19</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov22:2\">PRO 22:2</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas2:1-Jas2:4\">JAS 2:1–2:4</a></p>\n<h2>God brings good news for rich people</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps22:29-Ps22:31\">PSA 22:29–22:31</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt9:9-Matt9:10\">MAT 9:9–9:10</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark2:14-Mark2:15\">MRK 2:14–2:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke5:27-Luke5:29\">LUK 5:27–5:29</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt27:57\">MAT 27:57</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark15:43\">MRK 15:43</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke23:50-Luke23:51\">LUK 23:50–23:51</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke19:1-Luke19:10\">LUK 19:1–19:10</a></p>\n<h2>Examples of rich people</h2>\n<p>Abraham:\n <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen12:10-Gen12:16\">GEN 12:10–12:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen13:2\">GEN 13:2</a>; \n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen26:1-Gen26:14\">GEN 26:1–26:14</a> <em>Isaac</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen27:19\">GEN 27:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen27:28\">GEN 27:28</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen30:29-Gen30:43\">GEN 30:29–30:43</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen35:11-Gen35:12\">GEN 35:11–35:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen15:14\">GEN 15:14</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod3:22\">EXO 3:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod12:36\">EXO 12:36</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps105:37\">PSA 105:37</a>; \n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs10:23\">1KI 10:23</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr9:22\">2CH 9:22</a> <em>Solomon</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs20:13\">2KI 20:13</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr32:27-2Chr32:29\">2CH 32:27–32:29</a> <em>Joseph of Arimathea</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt27:57-Matt27:60\">MAT 27:57–27:60</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark15:43-Mark15:46\">MRK 15:43–15:46</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke23:50-Luke23:53\">LUK 23:50–23:53</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John19:38-John19:42\">JHN 19:38–19:42</a></p>",
